Category:Unidentified Jedi of the New Jedi Order

nodes.text: This unidentified Squib was a Jedi Apprentice in the New Jedi Order. During the Swarm War this individual was training to become a Jedi at the Ossus Academy. When Chiss Aristocra Chaf'orm'bintrano visited the academy, the apprentice was partaking in a game of Skorch.
